ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/roger-daltrey@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/roger-daltrey@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-who">谁人</a>乐队主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roger-daltrey">罗杰·达尔特雷 (Roger Daltrey)</a>分享了他对音乐会观众在参加演出前查找歌单的看法 - 请参阅下面他的说法。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roger-daltrey-on-teenage-cancer-trust-and-the-chances-of-new-music-from-the-who-3410696">罗杰·达尔特雷 (Roger Daltrey) 谈论青少年癌症信托基金以及 The Who 推出新音乐的机会</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rock/roger-daltrey-tour-scream-interview-1235703277/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a>采访时，达尔特雷谈到了他即将于明天（6 月 12 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-whos-roger-daltrey-announces-solo-north-american-tour-3603143">开始的北美个人巡演</a>。巡演期间，他将进行九场“半原声”演出，直至 6 月 28 日。门票现已通过<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Froger-daltrey-tickets%2Fartist%2F1335441" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ticketmaster</a>发售。 </p><figure id="attachment_3611606" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3611606" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3611606" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/roger_daltrey_2023.jpg" alt="罗杰·达尔特雷" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/roger_daltrey_2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/roger_daltrey_2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/roger_daltrey_2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/roger_daltrey_2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/roger_daltrey_2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/roger_daltrey_2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3611606" class="wp-caption-text">罗杰·达尔特雷. （马修·贝克/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>然而，达尔特雷拒绝透露他将在巡演中演奏的任何歌曲，然后他解释说互联网“毁了”他的音乐会：“太多人透露歌曲。如今的音乐会已经不再令人意外，因为每个人都想看歌单。我实在是受够了。互联网毁了我的现场表演。谁想知道接下来会发生什么？人们忘记了惊喜。我受不了了。”</p><p>当采访者建议粉丝们可能想计划一下上厕所时，达尔特雷回答道：“那为什么不开始在厕所里听血腥的节目呢？”</p><p>四月，Daltrey 的 The Who 乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-townshend">Pete Townshend</a>分享了告别巡演的最新消息，称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-who-pete-townshend-shoots-down-chances-of-a-farewell-tour-being-sarcastic-3618886">当他暗示这个想法时，他是在“讽刺”</a> 。最初，乐队似乎计划进行一场告别巡演，以轰动一时地结束他们的巡演日子，吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-townshend-says-the-who-have-one-final-thing-left-to-do-before-they-crawl-off-to-die-3609212">上个月表示，谁人乐队在退出之前还有“最后”一件事要做</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3570502" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3570502" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3570502" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/roger_daltrey_2024.jpg" alt="罗杰·达尔特雷" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/roger_daltrey_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/roger_daltrey_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/roger_daltrey_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/roger_daltrey_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/roger_daltrey_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/roger_daltrey_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3570502" class="wp-caption-text">罗杰·达尔特雷. （Katja Ogrin/Redferns 摄）</figcaption></figure><p>关于乐队即将结束的评论也是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-whos-roger-daltrey-at-80-i-have-to-be-realistic-im-on-my-way-out-3611539">罗杰·达尔特里 (Roger Daltrey) 上个月发表的评论的延续，当时他回顾 80 岁生日</a>，表示“他必须现实”并且“正在走出去”。</p><p>他还讲述了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-whos-roger-daltrey-stepping-down-as-teenage-cancer-trust-gig-curator-3567153">过去 20 年担任青少年癌症信托基金会慈善演出策展人的</a>经历（该活动已于今年结束），以及在最近的演出之前的紧张感。</p><p>同样，在一月份，达尔特雷接受了关于谁人乐队未来的采访， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roger-daltrey-on-the-whos-status-that-part-of-my-life-is-over-3570497">他在采访中表示，他“很高兴”“我生命中的那部分已经结束了”</a> ，然后澄清说，最终任何有关结束的决定都必须根据情况而定。与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-townshend">皮特·汤森德</a>一起制作。</p><p> 《谁人乐队》的罗杰·达尔特雷 (Roger Daltrey) 的帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-whos-roger-daltrey-is-fucking-sick-of-fans-researching-setlists-before-concerts-3764320">，粉丝们在音乐会前研究歌单，这让他们“他妈的厌烦了”</a> 。</p> ;
